data.description: Welcome to 3512 Wessex Lane located in Morrell Park area. This home features 3 bedrooms, 1 bath. Floor on the main level has been sanded and finished with wood natural color and high gloss coating beginning of the year. Living room has access to a private cozy deck to unwind from a hard day of work. Kitchen features porcelain floors with stainless steel appliances. Upstairs features 3 bedrooms and the bathroom. Downstairs is a finished basement with access to the backyard, laundry room and garage.   This property is currently tenants occupied, NEW OWNERS WILL TAKE OVER LEASE. LEASE DOES NOT EXPIRED UNTIL AUGUST 2024. AGENTS, PLEASE READ PRIVATE REMARKS BEFORE REQUESTING IN SHOWTIME. Showings are only Saturdays & Sundays from 12pm-5pm. Please schedule accordingly and respect Tenants' personal belongings.
